{
  "title": "Fragrant Yeasty Thai Kabanos Sausage Skewers",
  "description": "A light and flavorful Thai dish featuring kabanos sausages, perfect for a dinner party, this paleo-friendly recipe is cooked on a cedar plank to add a smoky flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Thai",
